                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18140420-98-off531 t18140420-98-crimeloc534"></join>. I lost my pantaloons on the 1st of April; I had not missed them until I found them at the pawnbrokers. The prisoner was a painter at work in my house. The constable searched him, and found the duplicates of the pantaloons on him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18140420-98-person972">
                  WILLIAM 
                  HAZARD
               <interp inst="t18140420-98-person972" type="surname" value="HAZARD"></interp>
